  "reference_number": "INU0236",
  "remarks": "\nIndustrial Factories of Precision Machinery (IFP) is or has been involved in a relevant nuclear activity, namely, being responsible for, engaging in, or facilitating, the development of a nuclear weapon delivery system in, or for use in, Iran. For this reason, Industrial Factories of Precision Machinery is an involved person within the meaning of the Iran (Sanctions) (Nuclear) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019.",
